snippet: Chelsea coach Jose Mourinho praised his hat-trick hero Samuel Eto'o, whose three goals buried Manchester United on Sunday, and gave himself some credit too for unexpectedly selecting the Cameroon striker....

headline.print_headline: Mourinho Praises Eto'o and His Tactics After Hat-Trick
headline.main: Mourinho Praises Eto'o and His Tactics After Hat-Trick

lead_paragraph: Chelsea coach Jose Mourinho praised his hat-trick hero Samuel Eto'o, whose three goals buried Manchester United on Sunday, and gave himself some credit too for unexpectedly selecting the Cameroon striker.
